@startuml
actor User
participant "Home Page" as Home
participant "Mock Test Service" as MockTestService
participant "Mock Test History Service" as MockTestHistoryService
participant "Test Interface" as Test

User -> Home : Selects Mock Test
Home -> MockTestService : Retrieve Test Details
MockTestService -> Home : Returns Test Details
Home -> User : Display Test Mode Options
User -> Home : Selects Test Mode
Home -> Test : Start Test in Selected Mode
User -> Test : Answers Questions
Test -> MockTestService : Record and Return Results
MockTestService -> MockTestHistoryService : Save Test History
Test -> User : Display Test Results
@enduml